race.comment: FRATIANNO (2) peaks and was tracking well before the latest. He will appreciate the longer sprint and is on a quick backup. BROADCAST BOOGIE (7) raced against the above last time and also disappointed. She was beaten a nose at Orange prior and that's the best measure of her chances. Steps up in distance and will get home hard. FOR THE BRAVE (8) went close at Dalby before a plain effort at Warwick. The blinkers come off, and she'd be in the finish at best. SOULS COMPANION (4) started $3.8 at Muswellbrook on debut and was never a winning hope. Had obviously been pleasing and the blinkers go straight on. Has a 2kg claim and the inside gate today, and quick improvement is on the cards.
